README file for the C++ implementation of the X-Trace core libraries.

This directory contains implementations of the X-Trace Metadata representation,
and facilities for propagating and reporting.

Requirements:
 - Python 1.5.2 or greater, for running the build tool, scons
 - scons 
 - Doxygen to generate the documentation

To build:
---------

In the src directory, type:

$ scons 

To clean up the generated files (similar to 'make clean'):
----------------------------------------------------------

$ scons -c

To build the documentation, 
---------------------------

$ scons doc

For more information, www.x-trace.net
